grep -i -n <files> <dir>
-i	:: for ignore case sensitity
-v	:: show lines whitch are not mached
-n	:: show line number
-w	:: show line with exact word
-c	:: count the no. of matches
-A 2	:: show 2 lines after the matched line
-B 2	:: show 2 lines before the matched line
-C 2	:: show 2 lines after and before the matched line




grep -r "abc" *		:: search recursively
